150 b. Education Support Personnel (K-12). A two percent
151 pay increase, beginning with the 2026-2027 fiscal year, shall
152 be given to each support worker employed full-time by the
153 Alabama Institute for Deaf and Blind. A separate local salary
154 schedule shall be established and maintained for each specific
155 job performed. The pay increase in this act shall be
156 incorporated into the support employees' salary schedules. The
157 base rate of pay for part-time support employees shall be
158 increased by two percent for the 2026-2027 fiscal year.
159 c. Miscellaneous Requirements. The AIDB board shall
