163 increase above to be given to each person employed for the
164 2026-2027 fiscal year and each year employed thereafter. The
165 pay increase contained in this subsection shall be paid to
166 each employee.
167 (4) Two-Year Postsecondary Institutions. The Board of
168 Trustees of the Alabama Community College System shall revise
