169 all salary schedules of the two-year postsecondary
170 institutions to reflect an increase of two percent for the
171 2026-2027 fiscal year. The pay increase shall be given to each
172 person employed in addition to any step increase to which the
173 employee is otherwise entitled. The Alabama Community College
174 System shall take proper steps to ensure that employees on all
175 salary schedules are given full credit for prior work
